Mario Longhi Filho's Biography



Mario Longhi received a Bachelor's degree in metallurgical engineering from the Institute Mau� de Tecnologica in S�o Paulo, Brazil in 1977. Mr. Longhi was elected: Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer of United States Steel Corporation in July 2012; President and Chief Operating Officer in June 2013; President & Chief Executive Officer and a Director in September 2013; and Chief Executive Officer and a Director on February 28, 2017.

 

